    Based on Syncfusion.Themes.FluentDark.WPF NuGet package:

    Core Theme Resources (automatically loaded by SfSkinManager):
    - Surface colors: SurfaceBackground, SurfaceForeground, SurfaceBorder
    - Content colors: ContentBackground, ContentForeground, ContentBorder
    - Primary colors: PrimaryBackground, PrimaryForeground, PrimaryBorder
    - Secondary colors: SecondaryBackground, SecondaryForeground, SecondaryBorder
    - Accent colors: AccentBackground, AccentForeground, AccentBorder
    - Interactive states: HoverBackground, PressedBackground, SelectedBackground
    - Disabled states: DisabledBackground, DisabledForeground, DisabledBorder
    - Semantic colors: ErrorBackground, WarningBackground, SuccessBackground
